						<h1>
															How to find the Document Root for your website / What directory should I put my files in?									</h1>
			
																
				
					<div style='font-size:12px; color:#aaa; margin-bottom:-10px; padding-top:5px;'>
							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;'><span style='color:#606060;'>Written by </span><a href='https://plus.google.com/102670474114655224886?rel=author'>Brad Markle</a></div>
							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;'><span style='color:#606060;'>Views:</span> <span name='page_views' id='page_views'>152,898</span></div>
							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;' title='Originally published: Aug 29, 2011'><span style='color:#606060;'>Published:</span> Jul 15, 2015</div>
							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;'><span style='color:#606060;'>Comments:</span> <a href='#comments'>60</a></div>
							<div style='clear:both;'></div>
						</div>
						</div>
	
		<div style='margin:0 0 10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #ddd;'>
			<table style='font-size:12px;'>
				<tr>
					<td valign='top'><strong>Discussions on this article:</strong></td>
					<td valign='top'><ul><li><a href='#comment-7422'>Can&#039;t find index.html - &quot;Website Coming Soon&quot;</a></li><li><a href='#comment-11045'>Can I change the document root?</a></li></ul></td>
